VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)/\w+/\{\w+\}
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(?i)\b(route|router|controller|handler|get|post|put|delete)\b
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of potential API endpoints in source code files, which may require special handling and validation.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for API Endpoint Detection.
